### 2.2 공통 모듈 — Mapper 확장 (신규 2개)

**파일:** `TACS/src/main/java/kr/or/tacs/common/notification/mapper/INotificationMapper.java`

기존 `selectTransportManagerIdByTrcNo` 다음에 추가:
```java
String selectWarehouseManagerIdByWirNo(@Param("wirNo") String wirNo);

String selectWarehouseManagerIdByCrrNo(@Param("crrNo") String crrNo);
```

**파일:** `TACS/src/main/resources/mybatis/mapper/common/INotificationMapper.xml`

기존 `selectTransportManagerIdByTrcNo` `<select>` 블록 다음, `<insert id="insertNotification">` 전에 추가. WAREHOUSE_MANAGER 산출은 7차의 `selectWarehouseManagerIdByIrNo` 와 동일한 `wh_in_rpt → wir_wm_id` 패턴 활용:

```xml
<select id="selectWarehouseManagerIdByWirNo"
        resultType="string">
    SELECT
        wir_wm_id
    FROM (
        SELECT
            w.wir_wm_id
        FROM wh_in_rpt w
        WHERE w.wir_no = #{wirNo}
          AND w.wir_wm_id IS NOT NULL
        ORDER BY w.wir_in_plan_dt DESC NULLS LAST, w.wir_no DESC
    )
    WHERE ROWNUM = 1
</select>

<select id="selectWarehouseManagerIdByCrrNo"
        resultType="string">
    SELECT
        wm_id
    FROM (
        SELECT
            w.wir_wm_id AS wm_id
        FROM cargo_release_req crr
        INNER JOIN wh_in_rpt w
            ON w.wir_gg_no = crr.crr_gg_no
        WHERE crr.crr_no = #{crrNo}
          AND w.wir_wm_id IS NOT NULL
        ORDER BY w.wir_in_plan_dt DESC NULLS LAST, w.wir_no DESC
    )
    WHERE ROWNUM = 1
</select>
```

> CRR → WIR JOIN 컬럼 (`crr.crr_gg_no = w.wir_gg_no`) 은 7차에서 발견된 `outbound_Mapper.xml` 패턴 참조. 실제 컬럼명이 다르면 자체 확인 후 정정. 다르면 보고하고 `WH_OUTBOUND_SCHEDULED` 정책 + 트리거 스킵.

